OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782910143
OL,3,CExeter University staff consider
OL,4,Cindustrial action over plans to cut
OL,5,C150 jobs
OL,7,FStaff at The University of Exeter are
OL,8,Fconsidering industrial action over
OL,9,Fplans to cut at least 150 jobs.
OL,11,FMembers of the University and College
OL,12,FUnion have already supported a no
OL,13,Fconfidence vote in the vice chancellor
OL,14,Fover what the union has described as
OL,15,F"vicious cuts".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
