FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782910143
OL,3,CExeter University staff consider
OL,4,Cindustrial action over plans to cut
OL,5,C150 jobs
OL,7,FThe University says the proposals
OL,8,Fcentre around the equivalent of 150
OL,9,Ffull-time roles, although the union
OL,10,Fclaims it will affect more than 200
OL,11,Fstaff, and around 500 have been told
OL,12,Fthey are at risk of redundancy.
OL,14,FThe union, UCU, fears that courses
OL,15,Fincluding history, English, modern
OL,16,Flanguages and politics will suffer
OL,17,Firreparable damage if the cuts go
OL,18,Fthrough.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782910143
OL,3,CExeter University staff consider
OL,4,Cindustrial action over plans to cut
OL,5,C150 jobs
OL,7,FThe union said cuts on the Falmouth
OL,8,Fcampus will also put the languages and
OL,9,Fenvironmental sciences provision at
OL,10,Fserious risk.
OL,12,FA petition against the cuts has
OL,13,Falready gained over 10,000 signatures.
OL,15,FA spokesperson for the University of
OL,16,FExeter said: "The University is
OL,17,Fconsulting with colleagues over
OL,18,Flimited and specific potential changes
OL,19,Facross some areas of our academic
OL,20,Ffaculties.
OL,26,@xD@NOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782910143
OL,3,CExeter University staff consider
OL,4,Cindustrial action over plans to cut
OL,5,C150 jobs
OL,7,F"It is important to stress that we are
OL,8,Fnot proposing to close any departments
OL,9,Facross our campuses. The proposals are
OL,10,Fin response to changes in demand, or
OL,11,Fwhere current activities are no longer
OL,12,Fsustainable.
OL,14,F"We have informed affected colleagues
OL,15,Fand are updating students and our
OL,16,Fwider community. We hope to achieve
OL,17,Fthese changes through voluntary
OL,18,Fmeasures and will continue working
OL,19,Fclosely with our community and trade
OL,20,Funions to avoid compulsory
OL,21,Fredundancies wherever possible.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782910143
OL,3,CExeter University staff consider
OL,4,Cindustrial action over plans to cut
OL,5,C150 jobs
OL,7,F"While Exeter remains in a strong
OL,8,Fposition, rising costs, the real-terms
OL,9,Fdecline in tuition fee income,
OL,10,Funderfunded research, and a sustained
OL,11,Fdrop in international student demand
OL,12,Fmean we must take action now.
OL,14,F"These changes are intended to secure
OL,15,Fthe University's long-term
OL,16,Fsustainability, protect our teaching
OL,17,Fand research excellence, and ensure
OL,18,Four activities remain aligned with
OL,19,Ffuture priorities."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU{D@SO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782910143
OL,3,CExeter University staff consider
OL,4,Cindustrial action over plans to cut
OL,5,C150 jobs
OL,7,FExeter UCU co-chair Michael J Flexer
OL,8,Fsaid: "In the biggest meeting in our
OL,9,Fbranch's history, our members have
OL,10,Foverwhelmingly voted no confidence in
OL,11,Fthe vice-chancellor and will be
OL,12,Fmeeting again imminently to begin
OL,13,Fpreparations for a strike ballot if
OL,14,Fmanagement refuses to change course.
OL,26,@pD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782910143
OL,3,CExeter University staff consider
OL,4,Cindustrial action over plans to cut
OL,5,C150 jobs
OL,7,F"Exeter University's stellar
OL,8,Fhumanities scholars are world renowned
OL,9,Fand have helped secure the
OL,10,Finstitution's status as one of the
OL,11,Fvery best in the UK. Making any one of
OL,12,Fthem redundant would be an
OL,13,Fextraordinary act of self-sabotage by
OL,14,Fmanagement.
OL,16,F"Axing over 200 jobs is no less than
OL,17,Facademic vandalism and would devastate
OL,18,Fstudent learning for years to come."
OL,26,@oD@AOUzD@dO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782910143
OL,3,CExeter University staff consider
OL,4,Cindustrial action over plans to cut
OL,5,C150 jobs
OL,7,FThe Union claims accounts show the
OL,8,Funiversity's reserves have increased
OL,9,Fby #188 million since 2023 and the
OL,10,Fnumber of staff earning more than
OL,11,F#100,000 has risen from 157 to 404.
OL,13,FUCU general secretary Jo Grady said:
OL,14,F"Management's claim that these cuts
OL,15,Fare needed because of financial
OL,16,Fpressures holds no water given
OL,17,FExeter's extremely healthy finances.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782910143
OL,3,CExeter University staff consider
OL,4,Cindustrial action over plans to cut
OL,5,C150 jobs
OL,7,F"There appears to have been no
OL,8,Ffinancial concerns whatsoever when it
OL,9,Fcomes to more than doubling the number
OL,10,Fof staff on six figure salaries. Those
OL,11,Fat the top now need to recognise the
OL,12,Fvaluable teaching and research our
OL,13,Fmembers carry out, halt these damaging
OL,14,Fcuts and work with us to avoid strike
OL,15,Faction."
OL,26,@wD@HO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
