FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782910143
OL,3,CExeter University staff consider
OL,4,Cindustrial action over plans to cut
OL,5,C150 jobs
OL,7,FThe Labour MP for Exeter, Steve Race,
OL,8,Fsaid: "The University of Exeter is a
OL,9,Fmajor economic driver of our city, and
OL,10,Fthe benefits of its research
OL,11,Fpartnerships with our local hospital,
OL,12,Fthe Met Office, and others bring real
OL,13,Fbenefits to everyone in our city. I
OL,14,Fwant to make sure it continues to play
OL,15,Fthat important role.
OL,26,@pD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782910143
OL,3,CExeter University staff consider
OL,4,Cindustrial action over plans to cut
OL,5,C150 jobs
OL,7,F"This will be a difficult time for the
OL,8,Femployees affected and I will do what
OL,9,FI can to support them. I visit the
OL,10,FUniversity regularly and have very
OL,11,Frecently met with trade union
OL,12,Frepresentatives to hear their concerns
OL,13,Fabout the University sector as a whole.
OL,15,F"I plan to meet again with employees,
OL,16,Funions, and the University leadership
OL,17,Fto understand the proposals, the
OL,18,Freasons behind them, and any possible
OL,19,Falternative ways forward."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU{D@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/11
